text: Emmerting is a municipality in Altötting in Bavaria in Germany and member of the administrative association of the same name. == Geography == === Geographical Place === Emmerting is in the southeast of Upper Bavaria. === Structure === Emmerting is divided into four parts: * Bruck * Oberemmerting * Seng * Unteremmerting There are also the subdistricts Altöttinger Forst, Alzgerner Forst, Emmerting and Holzfelder Forst. == References == == Other websites == * Homepage der Gemeinde * *
title: Emmerting
